| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5851 — Recovery Inhibition (gunra)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d1a5d21b-0e6f-54bb-9036-aa70d4bcf77c"
